n class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 bg-background-50/95 backdrop-blur-sm px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium shadow-sm\">⭐</span></div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-serif text-lg text-neutral-900 group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\">Reina Pepiada</h3><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0\">13.50<!-- -->€</span></div><p class=\"text-body-sm text-neutral-600 line-clamp-2\">L&#x27;incontournable : arepas au maïs, poulet rôti et avocat</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.1s\"><div class=\"group bg-background-50 rounded-card shadow-soft overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-medium hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden bg-background-100\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1626200419199-391ae4be7a41?w=600&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Empanadas\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105\" loading=\"lazy\"/><div class=\"absolute top-3 left-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 bg-background-50/95 backdrop-blur-sm px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium shadow-sm\">⭐</span></div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-serif text-lg text-neutral-900 group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\">Empanadas</h3><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0\">11.00<!-- -->€</span></div><p class=\"text-body-sm text-neutral-600 line-clamp-2\">Chaussons frits croustillants, fromage fondant ou bœuf</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.2s\"><div class=\"group bg-background-50 rounded-card shadow-soft overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-medium hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden bg-background-100\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1543339308-43e59d6b73a6?w=600&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Pabellón Criollo\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105\" loading=\"lazy\"/><div class=\"absolute top-3 left-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 bg-background-50/95 backdrop-blur-sm px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium shadow-sm\">⭐</span></div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-serif text-lg text-neutral-900 group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\">Pabellón Criollo</h3><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0\">21.00<!-- -->€</span></div><p class=\"text-body-sm text-neutral-600 line-clamp-2\">Le plat national : bœuf mijoté, haricots noirs, riz et plantain</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.30000000000000004s\"><div class=\"group bg-background-50 rounded-card shadow-soft overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-medium hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden bg-background-100\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1625937286074-9ca519d5d9df?w=600&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Cachapa Classique\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105\" loading=\"lazy\"/><div class=\"absolute top-3 left-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 bg-background-50/95 backdrop-blur-sm px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium shadow-sm\">⭐</span></div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-serif text-lg text-neutral-900 group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\">Cachapa Classique</h3><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0\">12.50<!-- -->€</span></div><p class=\"text-body-sm text-neutral-600 line-clamp-2\">Crêpe de maïs doux au fromage fondu, irrésistible</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.4s\"><div class=\"group bg-background-50 rounded-card shadow-soft overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-medium hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden bg-background-100\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551538827-9c037cb4f32a?w=600&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Mojito Caracas\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105\" loading=\"lazy\"/><div class=\"absolute top-3 left-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 bg-background-50/95 backdrop-blur-sm px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium shadow-sm\">⭐</span></div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-serif text-lg text-neutral-900 group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\">Mojito Caracas</h3><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0\">11.00<!-- -->€</span></div><p class=\"text-body-sm text-neutral-600 line-clamp-2\">Le cocktail signature : rhum, menthe, citron vert</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.5s\"><div class=\"group bg-background-50 rounded-card shadow-soft overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-medium hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden bg-background-100\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528207776546-365bb710ee93?w=600&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Quesillo\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105\" loading=\"lazy\"/><div class=\"absolute top-3 left-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 bg-background-50/95 backdrop-blur-sm px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium shadow-sm\">⭐</span></div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-2\"><h3 class=\"font-serif text-lg text-neutral-900 group-hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\">Quesillo</h3><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0\">7.50<!-- -->€</span></div><p class=\"text-body-sm text-neutral-600 line-clamp-2\">Flan vénézuélien au caramel, onctueux et réconfortant</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none;transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.4s\"><div class=\"text-center mt-12\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-semibold rounded-button transition-all duration-300 focus-visible:outline-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-500 to-secondary-600 text-white hover:from-secondary-600 hover:to-secondary-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] px-8 py-4 text-body-lg group relative overflow-hidden shadow-warm hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 animate-bounce-slow rounded-full flex items-center gap-2 relative\" href=\"/menu\"><span class=\"relative z-10\">Découvrir toute la carte</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform duration-300 animate-arrow-slide relative z-10\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><div class=\"absolute inset-0 -translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-full transition-transform duration-700 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent\"></div></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"histoire\" class=\"bg-background-100 bg-pattern py-section\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0s\"><div><p class=\"text-primary-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-3 text-center lg:text-left\">Notre Histoire</p><h2 class=\"font-serif text-display-md text-neutral-900 mb-6 text-center lg:text-left\">De Caracas à Levallois</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 text-neutral-600 text-body-lg leading-relaxed\"><p>Caracas Bar &amp; Tapas est né de l&#x27;amitié d&#x27;Igor et Difrines, deux passionnés souhaitant partager la richesse de la cuisine vénézuélienne avec les Parisiens.</p><p>Notre mission : vous faire voyager à travers les saveurs authentiques du Venezuela, depuis les arepas du petit-déjeuner jusqu&#x27;aux cocktails du soir.</p><p>Aujourd&#x27;hui installés à Levallois, nous perpétuons cette tradition d&#x27;accueil et de partage, où chaque plat raconte une histoire.</p></div><div class=\"mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200\"><h4 class=\"font-serif text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-4 text-center lg:text-left\">Petit lexique vénézuélien</h4><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0s\"><div class=\"bg-background-50 p-4 rounded-card shadow-soft\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-primary-600\">Arepas</span><span class=\"mx-2 text-neutral-400\">•</span><span class=\"text-neutral-600\">Galettes de maïs, grillées ou frites, fourrées selon les envies. La base de la cuisine vénézuélienne.</span></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.05s\"><div class=\"bg-background-50 p-4 rounded-card shadow-soft\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-primary-600\">Cachapa</span><span class=\"mx-2 text-neutral-400\">•</span><span class=\"text-neutral-600\">Crêpe épaisse à base de maïs doux, généralement servie avec du fromage fondu.</span></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.1s\"><div class=\"bg-background-50 p-4 rounded-card shadow-soft\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-primary-600\">Pabellón Criollo</span><span class=\"mx-2 text-neutral-400\">•</span><span class=\"text-neutral-600\">Le plat national : bœuf, haricots noirs, riz et plantain frit.</span></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.15000000000000002s\"><div class=\"bg-background-50 p-4 rounded-card shadow-soft\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-primary-600\">Tequeños</span><span class=\"mx-2 text-neutral-400\">•</span><span class=\"text-neutral-600\">Bâtonnets de pâte feuilletée fourrés au fromage, l&#x27;apéritif incontournable.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.2s\"><div class=\"relative\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1414235077428-338989a2e8c0?w=800&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Ambiance du restaurant\" class=\"rounded-card shadow-medium w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover\"/><div class=\"absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 lg:-bottom-6 lg:-right-6 bg-primary-500 text-white p-4 lg:p-6 rounded-card shadow-lg\"><p class=\"font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold\">2015</p><p class=\"text-xs lg:text-sm\">Année de création</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-background-100 py-section\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0s\"><div class=\"text-center group\"><div class=\"text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\">🍲</div><h3 class=\"font-serif text-heading-lg text-neutral-900 mb-3\">Cuisine Authentique</h3><p class=\"text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed\">Des recettes transmises, des produits frais, des saveurs du Venezuela</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.15s\"><div class=\"text-center group\"><div class=\"text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\">🍹</div><h3 class=\"font-serif text-heading-lg text-neutral-900 mb-3\">Cocktails Créoles</h3><p class=\"text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed\">Rhum, cachaca, pisco... des mélanges festifs et rafraîchissants</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.3s\"><div class=\"text-center group\"><div class=\"text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\">🎵</div><h3 class=\"font-serif text-heading-lg text-neutral-900 mb-3\">Ambiance Festive</h3><p class=\"text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed\">Musique latine, décoration chaleureuse, esprit de partage</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"galerie\" class=\"bg-background-50 py-section\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none;transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0s\"><div class=\"mb-12 text-center\"><p class=\"text-primary-600 font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3\">Un lieu vivant</p><h2 class=\"font-serif text-heading-xl text-neutral-900 mb-4\">L&#x27;Ambiance</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-600 text-body-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Découvrez l&#x27;atmosphère chaleureuse de Caracas Bar &amp; Tapas</p></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0s\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-card group col-span-2 row-span-2\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517248135467-4c7edcad34c4?w=800&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Ambiance du restaurant\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 aspect-square\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.08s\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-card group \"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559339352-11d035aa65de?w=800&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Cocktails colorés\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 aspect-square\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.16s\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-card group \"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565299624946-b28f40a0ae38?w=800&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Plat typique\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 aspect-square\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.24s\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-card group \"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550966871-3ed3cdb5ed0c?w=800&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Intérieur chaleureux\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 aspect-square\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.32s\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-card group \"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466978913421-dad2ebd01d17?w=800&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Fête et musique\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 aspect-square\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.4s\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-card group \"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514362545857-3bc16c4c7d1b?w=800&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Détail décoratif\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 aspect-square\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"privatisation\" class=\"bg-background-100 py-section\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none;transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0s\"><div class=\"mb-12 text-center\"><p class=\"text-primary-600 font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3\">Vos moments, nos saveurs</p><h2 class=\"font-serif text-heading-xl text-neutral-900 mb-4\">Privatisation &amp; Événements</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-600 text-body-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Des expériences uniques pour vos moments spéciaux</p></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0s\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-soft hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 h-full overflow-hidden group\"><div class=\"relative bg-amber-100 p-8 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"text-6xl transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\">🍹</div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/5 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8\"><h3 class=\"font-serif text-heading-lg text-neutral-900 mb-3\">Afterwork &amp; Tapas</h3><p class=\"text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Chaque jeudi, formules tapas à partager entre collègues ou amis. Ambiance musicale garantie.</p><div class=\"space-y-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-semibold rounded-button transition-all duration-300 focus-visible:outline-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-500 to-secondary-600 text-white hover:from-secondary-600 hover:to-secondary-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] px-8 py-4 text-body-lg w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-orange-600 text-white hover:opacity-90 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2\" href=\"/contact\"><span>Réserver un jeudi</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><p class=\"text-center text-sm text-neutral-500 font-medium\">Dès 19h • Jusqu&#x27;à 20 personnes</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.12s\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-soft hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 h-full overflow-hidden group\"><div class=\"relative bg-emerald-100 p-8 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"text-6xl transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\">🎉</div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/5 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8\"><h3 class=\"font-serif text-heading-lg text-neutral-900 mb-3\">Privatisation Étage</h3><p class=\"text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Notre étage peut accueillir vos événements jusqu&#x27;à 40 personnes. Formules sur mesure.</p><div class=\"space-y-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-semibold rounded-button transition-all duration-300 focus-visible:outline-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-500 to-secondary-600 text-white hover:from-secondary-600 hover:to-secondary-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] px-8 py-4 text-body-lg w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-secondary-600 text-white hover:opacity-90 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2\" href=\"/contact\"><span>Demander un devis</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><p class=\"text-center text-sm text-neutral-500 font-medium\">Étage privé • Jusqu&#x27;à 40 personnes</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.24s\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-soft hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 h-full overflow-hidden group\"><div class=\"relative bg-blue-100 p-8 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"text-6xl transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\">🍽️</div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/5 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8\"><h3 class=\"font-serif text-heading-lg text-neutral-900 mb-3\">Traiteur &amp; Cocktails</h3><p class=\"text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Nous apportons nos saveurs chez vous pour vos événements privés ou professionnels.</p><div class=\"space-y-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-semibold rounded-button transition-all duration-300 focus-visible:outline-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-500 to-secondary-600 text-white hover:from-secondary-600 hover:to-secondary-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] px-8 py-4 text-body-lg w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-primary-600 text-white hover:opacity-90 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2\" href=\"/contact\"><span>Nous contacter</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><p class=\"text-center text-sm text-neutral-500 font-medium\">Chez vous • Formules sur mesure</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none;transition:opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;transition-delay:0.5s\"><div class=\"mt-16 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511795409834-ef04bbd61622?w=1920&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Événement au restaurant\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white mb-4\">Un projet d&#x27;événement ?</h3><p class=\"text-white/90 text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Nous créons des expériences sur mesure pour vos moments spéciaux. Contactez-nous pour en discuter.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\"><a class=\"!bg-white !text-neutral-900 hover:!bg-white/90 hover:!scale-105 hover:!shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 rounded-full px-8 py-4 font-bold text-lg shadow-xl border-2 border-white/30 inline-flex items-center gap-2\" href=\"/contact\"><span>Demander un devis gratuit</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"tel:0123456789\" class=\"text-white/90 hover:text-white font-semibold flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors\"><span>01 23 45 67 89</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-background-100 py-section\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opaci